result.name: Fish & Chick

reviews.text:
Sadly all food (including the other two tables' food and soup) came from microwave, which was big shock to me. It was not peak hours so I don't see why they cannot fry by order when their menu emphasize on freshness and changing oil everyday.
They didn't even think of hiding the microwave...
Taste is good, reasonable price, good view~  but I don't think microwave food is the best way to keep reputation when deep fried food is suppose to be fast food already....
It's nice, but a little bit on the high side for a fish and chip lunch. Views are great though if you sit near the doors and can handle the summer heat.
Open view, airy, food is satisfactory. Took long for food to come. Good if you have time to enjoy.
Go to the place only for the view. Fish and chips are good but a little expensive. The tartar sauce is amazing.
The set meal for two is good value for money. Very yummy!
